<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Council of The Ancients - Dune Awakening Events</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.7.2/font/bootstrap-icons.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Orbitron:wght@400;700;900&family=Exo+2:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --dune-black: #0a0a0a;
            --dune-dark: #1a1a1a;
            --dune-orange: #ff6b00;
            --dune-orange-light: #ff8533;
            --dune-orange-dark: #cc5500;
            --dune-gold: #ffb366;
            --dune-text: #ffffff;
            --dune-text-muted: #cccccc;
        }

        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            background: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, var(--dune-dark) 0%, var(--dune-black) 70%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            font-family: 'Exo 2', sans-serif;
            color: var(--dune-text);
            position: relative;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        /* Arrakis planet in the background */
        .arrakis-planet {
            content: '';
            position: fixed;
            top: 10%;
            right: -20%;
            width: 600px;
            height: 600px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: 
                radial-gradient(circle at 30% 40%, 
                    #553311 0%, 
                    #995522 30%, 
                    #cc7733 50%, 
                    #ff9944 80%, 
                    #ffaa55 100%);
            box-shadow:
                0 0 60px rgba(255, 140, 0, 0.3),
                inset 30px -30px 100px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4),
                inset -30px 30px 100px rgba(255, 200, 150, 0.2);
            z-index: -2;
            opacity: 0.8;
        }
        
        /* Dust storm effect */
        .arrakis-planet::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: 
                url('data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="100" height="100" viewBox="0 0 100 100"><rect width="100%" height="100%" fill="none" /><rect x="0" y="0" width="1" height="1" fill="rgba(255,165,0,0.3)" /><rect x="10" y="30" width="1" height="1" fill="rgba(255,165,0,0.3)" /><rect x="20" y="50" width="1" height="1" fill="rgba(255,165,0,0.3)" /><rect x="30" y="70" width="1" height="1" fill="rgba(255,165,0,0.3)" /><rect x="40" y="40" width="1" height="1" fill="rgba(255,165,0,0.3)" /><rect x="50" y="20" width="1" height="1" fill="rgba(255,165,0,0.3)" /><rect x="60" y="60" width="1" height="1" fill="rgba(255,165,0,0.3)" /><rect x="70" y="30" width="1" height="1" fill="rgba(255,165,0,0.3)" /><rect x="80" y="80" width="1" height="1" fill="rgba(255,165,0,0.3)" /><rect x="90" y="10" width="1" height="1" fill="rgba(255,165,0,0.3)" /></svg>');
            opacity: 0.8;
            animation: rotate 120s linear infinite;
        }
        
        @keyframes rotate {
            0% { transform: rotate(0deg); }
            100% { transform: rotate(360deg); }
        }
        
        /* Animated background particles */
        body::before {
            content: '';
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: 
                radial-gradient(2px 2px at 20px 30px, var(--dune-orange), transparent),
                radial-gradient(2px 2px at 40px 70px, var(--dune-gold), transparent),
                radial-gradient(1px 1px at 90px 40px, var(--dune-orange-light), transparent),
                radial-gradient(1px 1px at 130px 80px, var(--dune-orange), transparent),
                radial-gradient(2px 2px at 160px 30px, var(--dune-gold), transparent);
            background-repeat: repeat;
            background-size: 200px 100px;
            animation: float 20s linear infinite;
            opacity: 0.05;
            z-index: -1;
        }

        @keyframes float {
            0% { transform: translateY(0px) rotate(0deg); }
            50% { transform: translateY(-20px) rotate(180deg); }
            100% { transform: translateY(0px) rotate(360deg); }
        }
        
        .navbar {
            background: rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.95) !important;
            backdrop-filter: blur(15px);
            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--dune-orange);
            box-shadow: 0 2px 20px rgba(255, 107, 0, 0.3);
            position: relative;
            z-index: 10;
        }
        
        .navbar-brand {
            color: var(--dune-text) !important;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-family: 'Orbitron', monospace;
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            text-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--dune-orange);
        }

        .navbar-nav .nav-link {
            color: var(--dune-text-muted) !important;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-family: 'Exo 2', sans-serif;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            padding: 0.8rem 1rem !important;
        }

        .navbar-nav .nav-link:hover {
            color: var(--dune-orange) !important;
            text-shadow: 0 0 5px var(--dune-orange);
        }

        .dropdown-menu {
            background: rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.95);
            border: 1px solid var(--dune-orange);
            backdrop-filter: blur(15px);
        }

        .dropdown-item {
            color: var(--dune-text-muted);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .dropdown-item:hover {
            background: rgba(255, 107, 0, 0.1);
            color: var(--dune-orange);
        }
        
        .hero-section {
            text-align: center;
            color: var(--dune-text);
            padding: 100px 0;
            background: 
                linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 107, 0, 0.1) 0%, transparent 50%),
                radial-gradient(circle at 50% 50%, rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.8) 0%, transparent 70%);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            position: relative;
        }

        .hero-section::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            background: 
                radial-gradient(circle at 20% 80%, var(--dune-orange), transparent 70%),
                radial-gradient(circle at 80% 20%, var(--dune-gold), transparent 70%),
                radial-gradient(circle at 40% 40%, var(--dune-orange-light), transparent 70%);
            opacity: 0.1;
            animation: heroGlow 8s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
        }

        @keyframes heroGlow {
            0% { opacity: 0.05; transform: scale(1) rotate(0deg); }
            100% { opacity: 0.15; transform: scale(1.1) rotate(5deg); }
        }
        
        .card {
            background: rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.9);
            backdrop-filter: blur(15px);
            border: 2px solid var(--dune-orange);
            border-radius: 20px;
            color: var(--dune-text);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(255, 107, 0, 0.2);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .card::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -2px;
            left: -2px;
            right: -2px;
            bottom: -2px;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, var(--dune-orange), var(--dune-gold), var(--dune-orange));
            z-index: -1;
            border-radius: 20px;
            opacity: 0.3;
        }

        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(255, 107, 0, 0.4);
        }

        .card:hover::before {
            opacity: 0.6;
        }
        
        .btn-discord {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--dune-orange), var(--dune-orange-dark));
            border: 2px solid var(--dune-orange);
            color: var(--dune-text);
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            padding: 15px 40px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-family: 'Orbitron', monospace;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(255, 107, 0, 0.4);
            text-shadow: none;
        }
        
        .btn-discord:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--dune-orange-light), var(--dune-orange));
            color: var(--dune-text);
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(255, 107, 0, 0.6);
        }
        
        .alert {
            border-radius: 15px;
            border: none;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            font-family: 'Exo 2', sans-serif;
        }

        .alert-danger {
            background: rgba(220, 53, 69, 0.2);
            border: 1px solid rgba(220, 53, 69, 0.5);
            color: #ff6b6b;
        }

        .alert-success {
            background: rgba(40, 167, 69, 0.2);
            border: 1px solid rgba(40, 167, 69, 0.5);
            color: #51cf66;
        }
        
        .dune-title {
            font-size: 4rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            font-family: 'Orbitron', monospace;
            text-shadow: 0 0 30px var(--dune-orange);
            color: var(--dune-text);
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
        }
        
        .guild-subtitle {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            color: var(--dune-orange);
            font-family: 'Orbitron', monospace;
            font-weight: 400;
            text-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--dune-orange);
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
        }
        
        .spice-accent {
            color: var(--dune-orange);
            font-weight: bold;
            text-shadow: 0 0 5px var(--dune-orange);
        }

        .lead {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            color: var(--dune-text-muted);
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
        }

        footer {
            background: rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.95) !important;
            border-top: 2px solid var(--dune-orange) !important;
            backdrop-filter: blur(15px);
            box-shadow: 0 -2px 20px rgba(255, 107, 0, 0.3);
        }

        footer a {
            color: var(--dune-orange);
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        footer a:hover {
            color: var(--dune-orange-light);
            text-shadow: 0 0 5px var(--dune-orange);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="arrakis-planet"></div>
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark">
        <div class="container">
            <a class="navbar-brand fw-bold d-flex align-items-center" href="/">
                <img src="/images/logo/logo-32.webp" alt="COA Logo" style="width:40px;height:40px;object-fit:cover;border-radius:50%;filter:drop-shadow(0 0 8px #ff8c00cc);">
            </a>
            <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarNav">
                <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
            </button>
            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
                <ul class="navbar-nav ms-auto">
                    <% if (typeof user !== 'undefined' && user) { %>
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link" href="/dashboard">
                                <i class="bi bi-calendar3 me-1"></i> Command Center
                            </a>
                        </li>
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link" href="/events">
                                <i class="bi bi-list-task me-1"></i> Operations
                            </a>
                        </li>
                        <li class="nav-item dropdown">
                            <a class="nav-link dropdown-toggle" href="#" id="navbarDropdown" role="button" data-bs-toggle="dropdown">
                                <i class="bi bi-person-circle me-1"></i> <%= user.username %>
                            </a>
                            <ul class="dropdown-menu">
                                <li>
                                    <form id="logoutForm" action="/logout" method="GET" style="display: inline;">
                                        <button type="submit" class="dropdown-item">
                                            <i class="bi bi-box-arrow-right"></i> Return to Desert
                                        </button>
                                    </form>
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                        </li>
                    <% } else { %>
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link" href="/login">
                                <i class="bi bi-box-arrow-in-right me-1"></i> Access Terminal
                            </a>
                        </li>
                    <% } %>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <main>
        <!-- Flash messages -->
        <div class="container mt-4">
            <% if (typeof messages !== 'undefined' && messages) { %>
                <% if (messages.error && messages.error.length > 0) { %>
                    <% messages.error.forEach(function(error) { %>
                        <div class="alert alert-danger alert-dismissible fade show" role="alert">
                            <i class="bi bi-exclamation-triangle me-2"></i> <%= error %>
                            <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="alert"></button>
                        </div>
                    <% }); %>
                <% } %>
                <% if (messages.success && messages.success.length > 0) { %>
                    <% messages.success.forEach(function(success) { %>
                        <div class="alert alert-success alert-dismissible fade show" role="alert">
                            <i class="bi bi-check-circle me-2"></i> <%= success %>
                            <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="alert"></button>
                        </div>
                    <% }); %>
                <% } %>
            <% } %>
        </div>

        <!-- Hero Section -->
        <section class="hero-section">
            <div class="container">
                <h1 class="dune-title">
                    Council of The Ancients
                </h1>
                <p class="guild-subtitle">
                    Guild Operations - Old Gods - Dune Awakening
                </p>
                <p class="lead mb-5">
                    Join your fellow Fremen in the conquest of Arrakis. <span class="spice-accent">The spice must flow.</span>
                </p>
                
                <% if (typeof user !== 'undefined' && user) { %>
                    <div class="card mx-auto" style="max-width: 600px;">
                        <div class="card-body text-center">
                            <h5 class="card-title">Welcome back, <span class="spice-accent">Fedaykin</span> <%= user.username %>!</h5>
                            <p class="card-text">The desert awaits your return. Check the latest guild events and coordinate with your fellow Ancients.</p>
                            <a href="/dashboard" class="btn btn-discord">
                                <i class="bi bi-calendar3 me-2"></i> Access Command Center
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                <% } else { %>
                    <a href="/login" class="btn btn-discord btn-lg">
                        <i class="bi bi-box-arrow-in-right me-2"></i> Access Terminal
                    </a>
                <% } %>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Features Section -->
        <section class="py-5">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                        <div class="card h-100 text-center">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <img src="/icons/events/spice_large_edited.avif" alt="Spice" style="width:40px;height:40px;object-fit:contain;margin-bottom:1rem;filter:drop-shadow(0 0 8px #ff8c00cc);">
                                <h5 class="card-title spice-accent">Spice Operations</h5>
                                <p class="card-text">Coordinate massive spice harvesting operations across the endless dunes. Control the most valuable resource in the known universe and secure your place among the Fremen.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                        <div class="card h-100 text-center">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <img src="/icons/events/explorationpoint_x2.avif" alt="Extraction" style="width:40px;height:40px;object-fit:contain;margin-bottom:1rem;filter:drop-shadow(0 0 8px #ff8c00cc);">
                                <h5 class="card-title spice-accent">Combat Missions</h5>
                                <p class="card-text">Execute strategic assault operations on enemy strongholds. Lead coordinated strikes with advanced tactics and Fremen ferocity.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                        <div class="card h-100 text-center">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <img src="/icons/events/TitaniumOre.avif" alt="Titanium" style="width:40px;height:40px;object-fit:contain;margin-bottom:1rem;filter:drop-shadow(0 0 8px #ff8c00cc);">
                                <h5 class="card-title spice-accent">Resource Acquisition</h5>
                                <p class="card-text">Mining expeditions for rare desert minerals and resources. Gather materials to strengthen the guild's position on Arrakis.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer class="text-center py-4 mt-5">
        <div class="container">
            <p style="color: var(--dune-text-muted);">&copy; 2025 Council of The Ancients. Created by <strong class="spice-accent">NylasDev</strong> - <a href="https://thevikingcompany.eu" target="_blank">The Viking Company</a></p>
            <p><small style="color: var(--dune-text-muted);">May your blade chip and shatter. <span class="spice-accent">The spice must flow.</span></small></p>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
